name: cockroaches
description: "What I most often remember from those days, besides the long hours spent at work, these are cockroaches. Every apartment where I lived then was teeming with them. I will never forget what a humiliation it was to bring my portfolio to Carmel Snow's office at Harpers Bazaar, open it and see a cockroach crawl out of there and crawl along the leg of the table. Carmel took pity on me and gave me a job." (—Å) Andy Warhol
